{"ts":"2026-04-30T14:56:53.834586+03:00","event":"tool_start","details":{"args":{"description":"Implement Task 339 per the masterplan. This task adds explicit, centralized policy metadata for every DSL AgentAction variant and remaining tool adapter. Currently `is_concurrency_safe` is hardcoded by tool name in `streaming_tool_executor.rs:17`, and no `ActionPolicy`/`ToolPolicy` struct exists. The plan introduces typed policy enums/types, wires them into `AgentAction`, replaces the hardcoded concurrency lookup, and adds runtime validation tests. Per the task requirements, `src/prompt_core.rs` and `TOOL_CALLING_SYSTEM_PROMPT` will NOT be modified.","steps":[{"description":"Move task file from pending to active per lifecycle protocol. `mv _tasks/pending/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification.md _tasks/active/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification.md`","expected_artifact_paths":["_tasks/active/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification.md"],"title":"Move Task 339 to active","verify_commands":["ls _tasks/active/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification.md"]},{"description":"Add policy types (ToolRisk, ToolExecutorState, ActionPolicy, etc.) to src/dsl/action.rs or a new src/dsl/policy.rs module. Define the enum variants for read-only, workspace-write, destructive, network, external-process risks, and executable/declaration-only/disabled states.","expected_artifact_paths":["src/dsl/action.rs","src/dsl/policy.rs"],"title":"Define policy metadata types for AgentAction","verify_commands":["grep -n 'ActionPolicy' src/dsl/action.rs src/dsl/policy.rs 2\u003e/dev/null"]},{"description":"Attach ActionPolicy metadata to every AgentAction variant (ReadFile, ListFiles, SearchText, SearchSymbol, EditFile, RunCommand, Ask, Done) with correct policy assignments per the task spec.","expected_artifact_paths":["src/dsl/action.rs"],"title":"Wire ActionPolicy into every AgentAction variant","verify_commands":["grep -c 'ActionPolicy' src/dsl/action.rs"]},{"description":"Replace the hardcoded `is_concurrency_safe(tool_name: \u0026str)` function in streaming_tool_executor.rs with a metadata-backed lookup that uses the new ActionPolicy.","expected_artifact_paths":["src/streaming_tool_executor.rs"],"title":"Replace hardcoded is_concurrency_safe with metadata lookup","verify_commands":["grep -n 'fn is_concurrency_safe' src/streaming_tool_executor.rs"]},{"description":"Update elma-tools ToolDefinitionExt to add compatibility policy types (ToolInterruptBehavior mapping) for remaining non-DSL adapters.","expected_artifact_paths":["elma-tools/src/registry.rs"],"title":"Add compatibility policy to elma-tools registry","verify_commands":["grep -n 'ToolInterruptBehavior' elma-tools/src/registry.rs"]},{"description":"Update tool_search (or its DSL-era path) so non-executable/declaration-only tools are not advertised as callable commands. Update tool_registry.rs filter logic.","expected_artifact_paths":["src/tool_registry.rs","src/tool_discovery.rs"],"title":"Filter declaration-only/disabled tools from callable lists","verify_commands":["grep -n 'ExecutorState\\|DeclarationOnly\\|Disabled' src/tool_registry.rs src/tool_discovery.rs"]},{"description":"Add runtime validation tests: every AgentAction variant has non-default policy, every model-callable action has an executor, disabled tools don't appear in callable definitions, concurrency-safe markings match read-only actions.","expected_artifact_paths":["src/dsl/action.rs"],"title":"Add policy validation tests","verify_commands":["grep -n '#[cfg(test)]' src/dsl/action.rs"]},{"description":"Run cargo fmt --check, cargo test (targeting agent_protocol, tool_registry, streaming_tool_executor), and cargo build.","expected_artifact_paths":[],"title":"Full verification: build and test","verify_commands":["cargo fmt --check","cargo test -p elma-tools tool_registry","cargo test agent_protocol tool_registry streaming_tool_executor","cargo build"]},{"description":"After successful verification, move the done task file to completed: mv _tasks/active/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification.md _tasks/completed/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification_DONE.md","expected_artifact_paths":["_tasks/completed/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification_DONE.md"],"title":"Archive Task 339 as completed","verify_commands":["ls _tasks/completed/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification_DONE.md"]}],"title":"Task 339: Action And Tool Metadata Policy Unification"},"tool":"enter_plan_mode"}}
