{"ts":"2026-04-30T14:57:07.517822+03:00","event":"tool_start","details":{"args":{"description":"Implement Task 339 per the masterplan. This task adds explicit, centralized policy metadata for every DSL AgentAction variant and remaining tool adapter. Currently `is_concurrency_safe` is hardcoded by tool name in `streaming_tool_executor.rs:17`, and no `ActionPolicy`/`ToolPolicy` struct exists. The plan introduces typed policy enums/types, wires them into `AgentAction`, replaces the hardcoded concurrency lookup, and adds runtime validation tests. Per the task requirements, `src/prompt_core.rs` and `TOOL_CALLING_SYSTEM_PROMPT` will NOT be modified.","steps":[{"description":"Move task file from pending to active per lifecycle protocol","expected_artifact_paths":["_tasks/active/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification.md"],"title":"Move Task 339 to active","verify_commands":["test -f _tasks/active/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification.md"]},{"description":"Add policy types (ToolRisk, ToolExecutorState, ActionPolicy) to a new src/dsl/policy.rs module and re-export from dsl/mod.rs","expected_artifact_paths":["src/dsl/policy.rs","src/dsl/mod.rs"],"title":"Define policy metadata types for AgentAction","verify_commands":["test -f src/dsl/policy.rs"]},{"description":"Attach ActionPolicy metadata to every AgentAction variant (ReadFile, ListFiles, SearchText, SearchSymbol, EditFile, RunCommand, Ask, Done) with correct policy assignments per the task spec","expected_artifact_paths":["src/dsl/action.rs"],"title":"Wire ActionPolicy into every AgentAction variant"},{"description":"Replace the hardcoded is_concurrency_safe(tool_name) function in streaming_tool_executor.rs with a metadata-backed lookup using ActionPolicy","expected_artifact_paths":["src/streaming_tool_executor.rs"],"title":"Replace hardcoded is_concurrency_safe with metadata lookup"},{"description":"Update elma-tools ToolDefinitionExt to add compatibility ToolInterruptBehavior mapping for remaining non-DSL adapters in registry.rs","expected_artifact_paths":["elma-tools/src/registry.rs"],"title":"Add compatibility policy to elma-tools registry"},{"description":"Update tool_registry.rs to filter declaration-only/disabled tools from callable tool definitions","expected_artifact_paths":["src/tool_registry.rs"],"title":"Filter declaration-only/disabled tools from callable lists"},{"description":"Add #[cfg(test)] module with tests: every AgentAction variant has non-default policy, disabled tools absent from callable lists, concurrency-safe markings match read-only actions","expected_artifact_paths":["src/dsl/action.rs"],"title":"Add policy validation tests"},{"description":"Run full build and focused tests: cargo fmt --check, cargo build, cargo test -p elma-tools, cargo test agent_protocol tool_registry streaming_tool_executor","expected_artifact_paths":[],"title":"Full verification: build and test","verify_commands":["cargo fmt --check","cargo build 2\u003e\u00261","cargo test -p elma-tools 2\u003e\u00261","cargo test agent_protocol tool_registry streaming_tool_executor 2\u003e\u00261"]},{"description":"After successful verification, move the done task file to completed","expected_artifact_paths":["_tasks/completed/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification_DONE.md"],"title":"Archive Task 339 as completed","verify_commands":["test -f _tasks/completed/339_Tool_Metadata_Policy_Unification_DONE.md"]}],"title":"Task 339: Action And Tool Metadata Policy Unification"},"tool":"enter_plan_mode"}}
